*Algorithm for partition:*

```
Partition(A, p, r)
{
   initialize x ← A[p];
   i ← p-1,  j ← r+1;
   while (i < j)
   {
      while (A[--j] > x)
      {
         while (A[++i] < x)
         {
            if (i < j) then
               Exchange(A[i], A[j]);
         }
      }
   }
   return j;
}

Exchange(A, i, j)
{
   p ← A[i];
   A[i] ← A[j];
   A[j] ← p;
}
```

